Subject: Make CLI status glyph skin-driven

The interactive footer still used the Hermes caduceus directly even when a
non-Hermes skin was active. Read a skin branding value for that compact status
symbol so the generated Argo skin can render a NadicodeAI-safe footer without
changing the default Hermes skin.

